                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>The evaluation of the bids was conducted in accordance with the provisions of the Conditions of Tender and Instructions to Bidders contained in the Bid document. The process involved examining the following of which this report is therefore based on:

A)	Completeness &amp; Responsiveness
B)	Detailed Evaluation
C)	Post Qualification
</Value>
